  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/e3886d73f9b1d068.jpg?v=1782535542\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I don't know about you but I have always been a fan of stickers. Puffy stickers, letter stickers, scratch and sniff stickers... you name it, I love it! Luckily, the apple didn't fall too far from the tree as Jack is equally as obsessed.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"1b-Pipsticks+Sticker+Subscription+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/196bfb1359bf50db.jpg?v=1782535545\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"1c-Pipsticks+Sticker+Subscription+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7b0e9deafa659379.jpg?v=1782535548\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>This is why are both such big fans of <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?B=827689&amp;U=530666&amp;M=63829&amp;urllink=\">Pipsticks</a> sticker subscription! Each month we get the cutest vellum envelopes packed with various stickers and the two of us have the best time going through each and every sheet.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"1d-Pipsticks+Sticker+Subscription+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6ef29597a291ba63.jpg?v=1782535550\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"1e-Pipsticks+Sticker+Subscription+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/bdae3a97f8a500c7.jpg?v=1782535553\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Each month's pack includes a postcard and Jack always takes his time carefully choosing the best stickers for embellishing. He told me that this particular postcard would be sent to his new baby cousin, Jake.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/73583430686c52ae.jpg?v=1782535556\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><a href=\"http://annmarieloves.com\">Ann-Marie</a>'s adorable son, Landon, was even there to supervise. </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/290f0496e63b7a41.jpg?v=1782535559\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I love supporting small businesses and <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?B=827689&amp;U=530666&amp;M=63829&amp;urllink=\">Pipsticks</a> is just about the coolest concept for stationery lovers like myself and Jack. Be sure to check them out!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
